N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7825.1 - Packaged terminal air conditioners

State Regulations

The standards for the energy efficiency ratio of packaged
terminal air conditioners are as follows: an energy efficiency ratio of 6.1 for
units manufactured after January 1, 1978; and 6.8 for units manufactured after

January 1, 1980. Notes
